description: Title and date supplied from M. Namba. Old maps in Japan, 1973, p. 200. Alternative title inferred from CiNii online, April, 9, 2020: Tenpō kaisei shinzō saiken Kyō ezu taizen, kan. Wood block print. Oriented with north to the left. Relief shown pictorially. Japanese. Pictorial map. LC copy annotated in black ink on cover: Seikyō chizu. Shows some dwellings of imperial families. Available also through the Library of Congress Web site as a raster image. Vault AACR2
